  • Klasse
    Beschreibung
    Continue
    The command telling QEMU to continue execution.
    ELFDump
    This class dumps the current memory data from a QEMU-instance to disk in ELF format.
    QueryBlock
    A command used to query QEMU for all available block devices.
    QueryCPU
    This command queries basic CPU information, like core count or architecture.
    QueryRegisters
    This command uses the "info registers" command from the human-monitor-interface to read the data from the registers and returns them as the objects.
    QueryTLB
    The command to query the QEMU-TLB and allow for finding of memory regions.
    Status
    The command to query basic status information about the running VM.
    Status.State
    An enum representing all states currently defined in the QMP protocol.f Simply copied from https://qemu-project.gitlab.io/qemu/interop/qemu-qmp-ref.html#qapidoc-83
    Stop
    The command telling QEMU to pause execution.
